<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.4.7">
<l>taṉma kaṉākavaṉ pēycci tāṉmulai yuṇṇak koṭukka</l>
<l>vaṉma kaṉāyava ḷāvi vāṅkimu laiyuṇ ṭanampī,</l>
<l>naṉma kaḷāymaka ḷōṭu nāṉila maṅkai maṇāḷā</l>
<l>veṉma kaṉēyamma muṇṇā yeṉṉammam cēma muṇṇāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a cruel demoness gave you her breast to suckle as her child,</l>
<l>Prince who, as a cruel child, suckled her breast, taking away her life,</l>
<l>Groom of the good lady, the herder girl, and of the lady of the four quarters,</l>
<l>My child, suckle my milk; suckle the treasure of my milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
